title: The Interviewer Becomes the Interviewee
description:
In a VERY SPECIAL EPISODE, Bill speaks with Assistant Editor Selena Cotte on challenges in technical writing. You'll hear how they came to journalism, how they prepare for shop stories, and how young writers should approach technical and niche reporting in a rare look behind the curtain at Electrical Apparatus Magazine!

Also, Selena will preview her cover story on Olsun Electrics (www.olsun.com), a Richmond, IL manufacturer of dry-type transformers, featured in the September issue of EA!

title: DarkspaceSytrus
description:
Darkspace Sytrus is the first track on the Retro Futuristic Neo-Spacehouse oriented EP of DDSM.
The DDSM EP will also feature the tracks Psychedelic Monkey and Koblenz Initiative. These Neo-Spacehouse tracks are also based on DieselPunk and Retro Futurism.

Neo-Spacehouse is a genre based on Retro Futurism ideology, which is a trend in the creative arts showing the bizare imagenation of the future produced by the creative minds of the previous century.

01 YO SOY ATABAL
description:
"Una canción que reúne el pasado con el futuro, “Yo Soy Atabal” es el nuevo sencillo (aquí incluyo el video oficial) del legendario grupo folclórico puertorriqueño Atabal.
“Yo Soy Atabal” es tanto un tributo a su fundador, Héctor Luis “Atabal” Rodriguez, como también a los ritmos folclóricos puertorriqueños que interpretan. En este caso, se resalta la Bomba."
-- Hector Aviles-  in Review
